{"id": 1030, "genre": 1001, "title": "你曾在公共场合面临过怎样的尴尬？ ", "description": "一次所有人共同见证的大型出洋相。（题图来自：Giselle Potter）", "record_count": 3948, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160703181354w8X6GPQAecqg4USK.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-06-16T11:00:14Z", "options": [{"id": 89344, "content": "听微信语音，不小心大声播出来了", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 272649}, {"id": 89345, "content": "宴会上把盐当做糖蘸，表情就亮了", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 635729}, {"id": 89347, "content": "拉肚子，冲去厕所蹲的太靠后，全喷地上了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 565391}, {"id": 89348, "content": "拉肚子，冲去厕所，蹲式，蹲的太靠后，全喷地上了，然后默默处理了一个小时。", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 565391}, {"id": 89349, "content": "拉屎没纸 找隔壁借发现是个女的", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 234461}, {"id": 115461, "content": "被一个陌生的熊孩子硬拖着去给他买了一个蛋糕。真事", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 755861}, {"id": 89350, "content": "平地摔2.0……戴耳机听歌太大声以为自己只是轻声哼其实…….公交上均得不行头倒来倒去，半梦半醒间控制自己忍住不要往边人上的肩膀上靠去……之类", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 633544}, {"id": 89351, "content": "隔壁班的女生和同学撞衫，光看背影没分出来，然后一手拍在她屁股上", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 640736}, {"id": 89352, "content": "感觉t台一样穿着高跟世界无我的在商场走 突然鞋子崴了 还被营业员看到", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 191998}, {"id": 89608, "content": "逛街的时候风太大 把裙子吹了起来", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 648582}, {"id": 89353, "content": "吃完粉挤电梯不敢呼吸，因为一嘴巴的大蒜味", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 597549}, {"id": 89354, "content": "裙子背后的拉链坏了浑然不知坐地铁", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 645263}, {"id": 89355, "content": "说了个自己觉得很搞笑的笑话，别人不笑。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 38, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 647498}, {"id": 97804, "content": "衬衫胸前扣子莫名爆开，一直不知道", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 152720}, {"id": 89357, "content": "公交车上睡着了靠在了别人肩膀上…", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 81918}, {"id": 89613, "content": "吃饭没带够钱?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 648599}, {"id": 90893, "content": "以为不穿bra不会有人看出来", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 651629}, {"id": 89614, "content": "突然发现自己裤子拉链没拉", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 648607}, {"id": 89359, "content": "坐公交卡没钱了，后面还有很多人等着上。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 644939}, {"id": 104210, "content": "带着耳机唱了出来", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 700756}, {"id": 89363, "content": "牵住了别人男朋友的手", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 647518}, {"id": 89364, "content": "因为人多尴尬假装给人打电话结果拿反手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 647520}, {"id": 89620, "content": "主动热情的和熟人打招呼，结果发现认错了人！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 459750}, {"id": 91924, "content": "裙子挂在内裤上", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 568350}, {"id": 89366, "content": "肚子咕噜噜叫", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 182814}, {"id": 89622, "content": "手机铃声是东京热开场曲！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 92714}, {"id": 89367, "content": "打喷嚏没拦住口鼻", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 182814}, {"id": 89368, "content": "憋尿憋太久 没憋住 讲真ˊ_>ˋ", "image": "img/option/option/20160702182740tYN5IjuPwUiDscGx.jpg", "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 646202}, {"id": 89624, "content": "带女生出去玩，坐地铁发现自己裤裆位置的白色污渍.....", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 363292}, {"id": 91674, "content": "摔倒，唱歌?走音。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 384836}, {"id": 89371, "content": "经常觉得自己 是这个世界上 最聪明的人！", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 647527}, {"id": 89372, "content": "看国服第一系列，结果开场曲是风骚的东京热，还没带耳机……", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 644346}, {"id": 89373, "content": "觉得别人太搞笑！！喷饭！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 507360}, {"id": 89885, "content": "夏天，走在大街上，不自觉的就硬了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 649288}, {"id": 89374, "content": "扑街", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 524425}, {"id": 89375, "content": "拉屎没有纸 旁边也没人 于是看见扔纸的桶里捡了点干净点的纸...", "image": null, "praise_count": 96, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 647532}, {"id": 89887, "content": "夏天，走在大街上，不自觉的就硬了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 649288}, {"id": 89376, "content": "迷路", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 643161}, {"id": 89378, "content": "在众人面前 pia  pia 的被台阶绊倒…。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 583791}, {"id": 100642, "content": "和同事不熟，自己遠遠坐著", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688332}, {"id": 95523, "content": "说话全程冷场", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668232}, {"id": 89380, "content": "大家原本都在谈笑风生，然后我强插进来讲了个冷笑话。没有然后。", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 583791}, {"id": 89384, "content": "电梯里放了一个很响的屁", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 498127}, {"id": 89640, "content": "在蛋糕店没拿好纸杯蛋糕摔在了地上", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 633604}, {"id": 89641, "content": "把人家老婆认成女儿", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 648627}, {"id": 83755, "content": "想偷偷拍照，发出很响的快门声", "image": null, "praise_count": 416, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 89387, "content": "说了很多话发现没人留意", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 549626}, {"id": 83756, "content": "最后一个上电梯，“滴滴滴”", "image": null, "praise_count": 281, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 83757, "content": "没仔细看文章，写了个很蠢的评论（还不能删", "image": null, "praise_count": 288, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 89389, "content": "偷偷拍照，结果有闪光", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 610956}]}